    <item>
      <title>摩根大通三名 CLO 银行家将离职加入三井住友银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/three-jpmorgan-clo-bankers-are-leaving-the-firm-to-join-smbc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三井住友金融集团 (Sumitomo Mitsui Financial Group Inc.) 正在从摩根大通 (JPMorgan Chase &amp; Co.) 聘请三名银行家，以扩大该日本公司的抵押贷款债务平台，因为今年这个规模约 1 万亿美元的市场活动激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/three-jpmorgan-clo-bankers-are-leaving-the-firm-to-join-smbc</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 21:30:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>供应过剩担忧加剧，必和必拓铁矿石产量小幅上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/bhp-s-iron-ore-production-in-first-quarter-edges-up-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团有限公司 (BHP Group Ltd.) 表示，其第一季度铁矿石产量较上年同期增长了 2%，主要矿商加大产量的举措加剧了供应过剩的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/bhp-s-iron-ore-production-in-first-quarter-edges-up-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 21:24:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耐克进军户外运动，寻找新的增长源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/nike-heads-outdoors-in-search-for-new-sources-of-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经历了艰难的一年后，耐克公司 (Nike Inc.) 正在寻找新的增长途径，正在准备在全球范围内大力推广其户外业务 All Conditions Gear，该业务主要生产防水靴、防撕裂夹克和背包等登山装备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/nike-heads-outdoors-in-search-for-new-sources-of-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 21:06:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛、摩根士丹利共计发行 110 亿美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/goldman-joins-jpmorgan-in-selling-bonds-after-reporting-earnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团和摩根士丹利周三共计出售了 113 亿美元的投资级债券，此前两家银行公布的盈利均超过了分析师的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/goldman-joins-jpmorgan-in-selling-bonds-after-reporting-earnings</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 14:02:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币逼近 70,000 美元，投机者瞄准创纪录高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/bitcoin-approaches-70-000-with-speculators-eyeing-record-highs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着对高风险资产和即将到来的美国大选的乐观情绪不断增强，比特币多头再次将目光投向了 3 月份创下的历史新高。]]></description>
